matrix structure, reusable-workflow architecture, and the specific tool choices
below) were identified by inspecting the public, MIT/Apache/BSD-licensed
repositories of the following organizations via the GitHub REST API. No content
was copied verbatim from any of these repositories; each is cited by name in the
relevant reusable workflow's header comment and in docs/research/. Full findings
